otilia_piano wrote a review Jan 2024
Singapore, Singapore182 contributions
Great stay in Danang
Exceptional hotel for families! We had a 2 bedroom apartment and the hotel could provide a cot for our baby. The location is ideal, just across the beach, and close to many restaurants. The hotel is very clean, the breakfast is exceptional with a large area of choice, the staff are very friendly, there is a bar, gym, pool and spa at the top floor. There is even a small indoor play area close to the restaurant (not a very good supplies of toys, but it could keep my baby busy while we took our breakfast). We really enjoyed our stay at this hotel and we strongly recommend it!
