Excellent Stay
We had a great stay at A La Carte Da Nang Beach. Rooms were spacious, clean and comfortable, and the hotel was centrally located and convenient to everywhere we wanted to go. The breakfast buffet was spectacular. The hotel provided us with a late check-out on our last day for no additional charge, which was greatly appreciated so that we would not have to kill several additional hours somewhere before our flight. Highly recommend!
